## ğŸ“š API Reference

### HÃ m tiá»‡n Ã­ch chÃ­nh

#### `get_image_info(image_path)`
Láº¥y thÃ´ng tin cÆ¡ báº£n vá» áº£nh.

**Tham sá»‘:**
- `image_path` (str): ÄÆ°á»ng dáº«n Ä‘áº¿n áº£nh

**Tráº£ vá»:**
```python
